      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 5, United States Code, to provide for the issuance of a prisoner-of-war medal to civilian employees of the Federal Government who, during war or under wartime conditions, are taken captive by armed forces or agents of a foreign government hostile to the United States.</title>
      </item>
